question: Display female laboratory technicians and research scientists.
sql_query1:
SELECT Research_Scientists.name
FROM Research_Scientists
WHERE Research_Scientists.Gender = "Female"
UNION
SELECT Laboratory_Technicians.name
FROM Laboratory_Technicians
WHERE Laboratory_Technicians.Gender = "Female"
sql_query2:
SELECT Research_Scientists.name
FROM Research_Scientists
UNION
SELECT Laboratory_Technicians.name
FROM Laboratory_Technicians
WHERE Laboratory_Technicians.Gender = "Female"
interpretation1: Can you show female research scientists and female laboratory technicians?
interpretation2: List all research scientists and also display female laboratory technicians.
